title: Huawei Switches: Fans
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/huawei
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the fan speed in percentage of Huawei switches.

 It supports the stacking function in which multiple devices are connected
 together to logically function as one device.

 Upper and lower levels can be configured in WATO.

item:
 The stack member number, followed by slash (/), followed by a consecutive number for each
 fan of this member.

discovery:
 One service is created for each fan of each stack member.
